library(plyr)
library(ggplot2)
Dep = count(Data$Department)
Dep<- Dep[order(Dep$freq),]
Dep$x <- factor(Dep$x, levels = Dep$x[order(-Dep$freq)])
ggplot(data=Dep, aes(x=x, y=freq, fill='red'))+geom_bar(stat='identity')
